Title: Reduction of Quantum Entropy by Reversible Extraction of Classical Information  
Author: Charles H. Bennett, () Gilles Brassard, () Richard Jozsa, ();(a) Dominic Mayers, () Asher Peres, ();(b) Benjamin Schumacher, () and William K. Wootters () 
